S.FORM: Tuilaepa Lupesoliai Sailele Malielegaoi u siwkay niza u pilecuhan ni Tuilaepa Lupesoliai Sailele Malielegaoi i Lepa nu Samoa. nalecuhan ciniza i 4 a bulad 14 a demiad 1945 a mihcaan. pahezekay niza i tabakiay a cacudadan nu Auckland (University of Auckland ). micakat u cunli ( Prime Minister) nu Samoa ayza sa ci Tuilaepa Lupesoliai Sailele Malielegaoi, micakat a demiad sa i 1998 a mihcaan 11 bulad 23 demiad. u ngangan niza u sulit tu ngangan nu Amilika a kamu:Tuila'epa Lupesoliai Neioti Aiono Sa'ilele Malielegaoi u sulit tu ngangan nu hulam a kamu: u sulit tu ngangan nu Sakizaya a kamu:Tuyilaaypa Sayilaylay Maliaylayelawyi u sapuyaay a kakuniza kakuniza malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government Tuila'epa Lupesoliai Neioti Aiono Sa'ilele Malielegaoi
